<h2>Premiere Service</h2>
<p>
The Soybean And Corn Advisor offers a Premier Service for our clients who require up-to-the-minute information concerning market conditions.  This service encompasses not only the weekly Newsletter; it also includes frequent and unlimited phone contact with our clients as well.  The Soybean And Corn Advisor prides itself on personalized service and programs can be tailored to meet each client's individual needs.
</p>

<h2>Presentations</h2>
<p>
Dr. Cordonnier has been a popular speaker at numerous agricultural related events for more than 25 years.  He brings to his audiences an extensive knowledge of South American agriculture gained by 35 years of living and working in South America.
</p>

